==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: To hold hands with both parties.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī shǒu tuō liǎng jiā

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[手]][[托]][[兩]][[家]]'''

# To serve as an honest broker between two parties.

